Here we have doing this by three approaches: [follow SS for detailed info.]
1] using spring jdbc
2] using jpa with hibernate
3] using spring data

==========================
1] using spring jdbc:
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/SpringJdbcApplication.java
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/jdbc/PersonJdbcDao.java
==========================
2] using jpa with hibernate:
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/SpringJpaApplication.java
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/jpa/PersonJpaRepository.java
==========================
3] using spring data:
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/SpringDataApplication.java
/spring-database/src/main/java/com/yolo/spring/springdatabase/springdata/PersonSpringDataRepository.java

